## Quick Decision Guide

**I'm a student/researcher:**
‚Üí Use PolyForm Noncommercial ([LICENSE-NONCOMMERCIAL.md](LICENSE-NONCOMMERCIAL.md))

**I'm a hobbyist/maker:**
‚Üí Use PolyForm Noncommercial ([LICENSE-NONCOMMERCIAL.md](LICENSE-NONCOMMERCIAL.md))

**I run a small drone business (< 10 drones):**
‚Üí Check if you meet Small Business thresholds ([LICENSE-SMALL-BUSINESS.md](LICENSE-SMALL-BUSINESS.md))
‚Üí If yes: Free to use
‚Üí If no: Contact for commercial license

**I run drone shows with 10+ drones:**
‚Üí Contact for commercial license ([LICENSE-COMMERCIAL.md](LICENSE-COMMERCIAL.md))

**I'm a large enterprise:**
‚Üí Contact for commercial license ([LICENSE-COMMERCIAL.md](LICENSE-COMMERCIAL.md))

**Still unsure?**
‚Üí Email p30planets@gmail.com with your use case

